{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙率队穿越草原丘陵，察觉嚣魏牟可能设伏于前方峡谷。他命令清除草木、挖掘水坑、联车为阵，做好防火准备。少原君反对部署，辱骂乌卓，被项少龙和成胥驳斥。少原君欲带家将离去，平原夫人怒打其耳光，母子决裂。夜间敌人果然来袭，项少龙先发制人以火箭引燃预洒灯油的林木，大火将敌军卷入火海。敌人被逼强攻营地，遭乱箭射杀，几乎全军覆没，项少龙不损一兵一卒大获全胜。战后队伍抵达濮水西岸扎营休整，平原夫人向项少龙吐露心声，请求他给自己一个孩儿，但坦言已安排改嫁魏国大将。此时关朴援兵抵达。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假若我猜得不错，嚣魏牟和他的人定在峡谷里等待我们。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_xu",
      "speaker_name": "成胥",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "探子的回报说，若有人埋伏两边崖壁上，只是掷石便可使我们全军覆没。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zha_yuan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "查元裕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这里处处丘峦草树，敌人若在上风处放火，只是那浓烟便可把我们活活呛死。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zha_yuan_yu",
      "text": "浓烟只能对付没有预备的人，元裕你立即发动全部人手，将这个山头和斜坡的草树全部除去，又在坡底挖掘深坑，引附近的溪流进坑里，把营地团团围着。山头则联车为阵，保护营地。同时营地里准备大量清水，每营至少两桶，每人随身带备布巾一类的东西，遇上浓烟时，沾水后盖在脸上，便可不怕烟呛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zha_yuan_yu",
      "text": "吩咐所有人把战甲脱下，免得影响行动！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！为何停在这么危险的地方？怎样对抗敌人的火攻？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你喜欢的话，便自己过峡谷吧！恕我不奉陪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "进既不能，理应后撤至安全地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "尚有三个时辰日落，山路难走，若撤至进退不得的地方，不若……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "闭嘴！哪有你这奴才插嘴的资格。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "公子弄错哩！乌卓是我的战友，他的话便等若我的话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_xu",
      "speaker_name": "成胥",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "谁说的话有道理，我们便听谁的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "能和孙姑爷并肩作战，实是生平快事。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cheng_xu",
      "text": "只要守过今晚，我有把握对付嚣魏牟布在峡谷上的伏兵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_xu",
      "speaker_name": "成胥",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "照我估计，嚣魏牟的人手绝不会比我们多，否则早在路上对我们强攻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "想问我和赵倩的关系，放心吧！她仍是处子之身。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可是你挑起她的情火，她怎肯嫁到魏国去，我们还到大梁干什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "自然是去偷《鲁公秘录》哩！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "我知你想说若信陵君明知我们要去偷他的《秘录》，自不会教我们得手，是吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "信任你的夫君吧！在这尔虞我诈的时代，只可随机应变，说不定鱼与熊掌，两者兼得。嘿！我好像很久没有和你行房了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是没有'行营'，哪来'房'呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小紫",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "成副将有请项爷立即出去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "定是少原君这家伙又闹事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "我才不陪蠢人送死，这里山林处处，敌暗我明，我们能守多久？只有对军事一无所知的愚人，才会做这和自杀相差无几的蠢事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你有什么资格批评人呢？你能破灰胡的大军吗？那天灰胡攻来，你除了躲在帐内，做过什么出色的事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "好！现在你完全站在外人处了，还反过头来对付自己的儿子，由今天开始，我再没有你这种娘亲。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你给我再说一次！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "有了奸夫，还要我这儿子做啥！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "少原君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩儿们！要活命的随我去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁也不准随他去，这个家仍是由我作主，何时轮到他说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_shao_yuan_jun",
      "text": "你若不给我叩头认错，休想我原谅你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若要活命，立即给我去工作。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嚣魏牟，你中计哩！放箭！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你为何不下水畅泳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "若夫人肯和我鸳鸯戏水，下属自当奉陪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我愈来愈佩服你，若长平一战是你做主帅，保证死的四十万人不是赵人而是秦兵，整个形势亦会改写。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人过誉了，偶有小胜，何足挂齿。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "少原君怎样了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要提那没用的畜生。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "他竟敢不向你叩头认错吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "叩头认错有什么用？我一向已对先夫不大满意，岂知这畜生更远不如他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你肯否给我一个孩儿，只要他有一半像你，妾身已心满意足。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "到此刻我才真正感受不到夫人对我的敌意。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是你以本领赚回来的，连番目睹你鬼神莫测的手段后，我再不想成为你的敌人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "那你是否想成为我的女人呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在我什么都不想瞒你，今天我返回魏国，早安排好改嫁一名握有兵权的大将，这是不能更改的事。你……你怪我吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "关朴的援兵来哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    }
  ],
